    [∀ i, NormedAddCommGroup (E i)] [∀ i, InnerProductSpace ℝ (E i)] [∀ i, MeasurableSpace (E i)]
    [∀ i, CompleteSpace (E i)] [∀ i, BorelSpace (E i)] [∀ i, SecondCountableTopology (E i)]
